  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess short and long term outcomes of individuals undergoing minimally
      invasive surgery of the gastro-esophageal junction (MISGEJ). Patients will respond to
      questionnaires on an annual basis evaluating quality of life and functionality following
      MISGEJ. Hospital charts will also be reviewed on an annual basis to assess patient health
      outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
